or an organisation.

127
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:47,960
We also mentioned that Catherine was no fashion victim,

128
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:50,920
a person who has to follow the latest fashion trends.

129
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:54,160
Rummaging was a word that described searching for something

130
